briefTitle: A Study of LY2963016 Compared to Lantus® in Adult Chinese Participants With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus
officialTitle: A Prospective, Randomized, Open-Label Comparison of a Long-Acting Basal Insulin Analog LY2963016 to Lantus® in Adult Chinese Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus
summary: The purpose of this study is to compare long-acting basal insulin analog LY2963016 to Lantus® in insulin naïve adult Chinese participants with Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus (T2DM) on 2 or more oral antihyperglycemic medications (OAMs). Participants will continue their OAMs throughout the study.

primaryOutcome.measure: Change From Baseline in Hemoglobin A1c (HbA1c) (LY2963016 to Lantus®)
